  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">10,000 Beds coordinates addiction treatment scholarships for addicts who desperately need and want help but are completely without resources. Our application process is rigorous and serves as a screening and placement process that most treatment programs do not have the resources to conduct for scholarship awardees. 10,000 Beds provides a dual service: 1) by helping addicts find the right treatment and 2) by helping treatment centers scholarship their empty beds with the right candidates.</narrative>
